(1597, 1, '2018-11-05 15:14:34', '2018-11-05 15:14:34', '<p>[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" css=\".vc_custom_1541385753293{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1541385829597{padding-top: 200px !important;padding-bottom: 160px !important;background-image: url(http://papyrus.wedoweb.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/home-3.jpg?id=1625) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Eat like an egyptian\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:72px|text_align:center|color:%23ffe786\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Asul%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\" el_class=\"text-uppercase\"][vc_single_image image=\"1627\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css=\".vc_custom_1541385786781{margin-bottom: 21px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1541430683776{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;background-color: #ffe786 !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1541429286400{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Egyptian Food is an Exquisite Taste of History.\" font_container=\"tag:h6|font_size:26px|text_align:center|color:%234d7a39|line_height:32px\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1541429056069{margin-bottom: 22px !important;}\" el_class=\"text-bold\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"At Papyrus, it’s Simply Fresh and Delicious<br />\nFood Every Day.\" font_container=\"tag:h1|font_size:40|text_align:center|color:%234d7a39|line_height:46px\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1541429658227{margin-bottom: 44px !important;}\" el_class=\"text-bold\"][vc_single_image image=\"1626\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css=\".vc_custom_1541429264014{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1541429181879{margin-bottom: 40px !important;padding-right: 180px !important;padding-left: 180px !important;}\" el_class=\"text-custom1\"]</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Papyrus offers Egyptian vegetarian food based on deliciously-authentic and traditional recipes. Egyptians have a rich agricultural history that dates back thousands of years. That deep connection to the land, the abundance of fresh ingredients, and their love for good food allowed Egyptians to explore and perfect vegetarian food over the ages.</p>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1541430750790{padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-image: url(http://papyrus.wedoweb.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/home-2.jpg?id=1624) !important;}\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1541388937565{padding-top: 0px !important;}\"][vc_row_inner equal_height=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1541430550903{padding-top: 0px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"2/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Discover Amazing Flavours Based on Family Recipes made with Fresh, Natural Ingredients.\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:40|text_align:left|color:%23ffe786|line_height:46px\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Asul%3Aregular%2C700|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text-custom2\"]At Papyrus, we feel that Egyptian vegetarian food is more relevant today than ever, because it’s delicious, healthy, and environmentally sensible. From transforming the humble bean into a rich staple food to creating distinct flavours and combinations of savoury and fresh ingredients, Egyptian vegetarian food is renowned for its flavours, texture, and use of fresh herbs.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_btn title=\"View Menu\" shape=\"square\" color=\"green\" align=\"center\" css=\".vc_custom_1541430646353{padding-top: 40% !important;background-color: #4d7a39 !important;}\" el_class=\"btn-custom1\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Fpapyrus.wedoweb.co%2Fmenu%2F|||\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" equal_height=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1541380340082{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;background-color: #4d7a39 !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1541430809965{padding-right: 30px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;background-image: url(http://papyrus.wedoweb.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/home-1.jpg?id=1623) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1541379817451{padding-right: 100px !important;padding-left: 100px !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Explore Exotic Foods\" font_container=\"tag:h1|font_size:40|text_align:left|color:%23ffe786|line_height:46px\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1541430869908{margin-top: 1px !important;margin-bottom: 43px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"220\" img_size=\"full\" css=\".vc_custom_1489743761202{margin-bottom: 21px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]Egypt was at the crossroads of trade, and throughout its history, welcomed people from other cultures who brought along exotic cooking ingredients and preparation techniques. Fine desserts made with mastic and pistachios were surely the outcome of an open society that welcomed people from Europe and the Levant to call Egypt their home.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1541380457387{border-top-width: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"][pm_vc_custom_map custom_map_code=\"\" custom_map_height=\"470px\" custom_css=\".vc_custom_1541378192437{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n', 'Home 1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '547-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-11-05 15:14:34', '2018-11-05 15:14:34', '', 547, 'http://papyrus.wedoweb.co/?p=1597', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
