\".vc_custom_1489744065436{margin-bottom: 65px !important;padding-top: 63px !important;padding-bottom: 63px !important;background-image: url(http://pixel-mafia.com/demo/wordpress-themes/vincent/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2017/02/back_1.jpg?id=247) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1489743552413{padding-right: 30px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"We Are Legend\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:left|color:%23121618\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1489743693917{margin-top: 1px !important;margin-bottom: 43px !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"we don’t just make pizza. We make people’s days. Vincent Pizzeria was built on the belief that pizza should be special, and we carry that belief into everything we do.\" font_container=\"tag:h6|text_align:left|color:%23121618|line_height:32px\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1489743721499{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"220\" img_size=\"full\" css=\".vc_custom_1489743761202{margin-bottom: 21px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"color: #121618;\">What’s our purpose at Vincent? Moments of Excitement. All made possible by our flavor, innovation and, most importantly, by unlocking potential in our team members.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #121618;\">With more than 50 years of experience under our belts, we understand how to best serve our customers through tried and true service principles. Instead of following trends, we set them. We create food we’re proud to serve and deliver it fast, with a smile. No matter where you find us, we’re making sure each meal our customers enjoy is delicious and one-of-a-kind.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1489743877394{padding-right: 0px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;}\"][pm_vc_blockquote blockquote_view_type=\"type_2\" blockquote_author_image=\"253\" blockquote_author_avatar=\"true\" blockquote_author=\"Adam Jefferson\" blockquote_author_position=\"Lawyer, New York\" custom_css=\".vc_custom_1489743868245{margin-bottom: 42px !important;}\"]<span style=\"color: #121618;\">Vincent was one of the first restaurants I discovered upon moving to New York last summer, and it remains a favorite. Despite its sizable menu full of pastas, sandwiches, and pizzas, I almost always get the same thing – the Vincent pizza. It\'s made with Ricotta &amp; Marinara sauces, spiced with oregano, and topped with eggplant, red onions, basil, Pecorino Romano &amp; Mozzarella. It really is one of the best pizzas I\'ve ever had – and I eat a lot of pizza.</span>[/pm_vc_blockquote][pm_vc_blockquote blockquote_view_type=\"type_2\" blockquote_author_image=\"255\" blockquote_author_avatar=\"true\" blockquote_author=\"Samantha Greenberg\" blockquote_author_position=\"Artist, Boston\"]<span style=\"color: #121618;\">The pizza is delicious! The crust is thin and crispy, great sauce, and awesome cheese blend. And it makes a cute cheap date!</span>[/pm_vc_blockquote][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Discover our menu\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1490177415654{margin-bottom: 39px !important;}\"][pm_vc_product_listing product_listing_items=\"8\" product_first_category=\"29\" custom_css=\".vc_custom_1520033329515{margin-bottom: 57px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1490193190451{margin-bottom: 59px !important;padding-top: 67px !important;background-image: url(http://pixel-mafia.com/demo/wordpress-themes/vincent/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2017/03/back_3.jpg?id=459) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Not just a pizza, but Lifestyle\" font_container=\"tag:h6|text_align:center|color:%23121618\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1490178054254{margin-bottom: 22px !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Something From the Blog\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:center|color:%23121618\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1490178109710{margin-bottom: 44px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"220\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css=\".vc_custom_1490178142567{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1490192700497{margin-bottom: 40px !important;padding-right: 180px !important;padding-left: 180px !important;}\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #121618;\">And yes, we’re pizza people. But we’re also human people, we lead with our hearts, we believe in giving back to the global community. Join us, welcome to Our Blog!</span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][pm_vc_blog posts_per_page=\"4\" blog_view_type=\"simple\" columns=\"4\" blog_text_color=\"#121618\" blog_title_color=\"#121618\" button_text_color=\"#121618\" button_hover_color=\"#ffffff\" button_bg_hover=\"#121618\" button_border_color=\"#121618\" button_border_hover=\"#121618\" custom_css=\".vc_custom_1491481430133{margin-bottom: 80px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Subscribe for Our Newsletter\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1490195034270{margin-bottom: 54px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1490195643194{margin-bottom: 85px !important;}\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[contact-form-7 id=\"744\" title=\"Subscribe Form\"]</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\"][vc_column][pm_vc_custom_map custom_map_code=\"\" custom_map_height=\"470px\" custom_css=\".vc_custom_1532356076017{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home 1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '547-revision-v1', '', '